N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7862.1 - General

State Regulations

This Part sets forth information filing requirements, as
determined by the board or by the chair as authorized by the board, applicable
to major biogas and biofuel producers, and major biomass suppliers or
processors and any other entity that the board deems appropriate to collect
such information. Notes
